Dr. Speller: Dual enrollment in #EarlyCollege does not override state requirements for graduation. #EdChat
Dr. Williams: #PellGrants are applied retroactively. Once college credits are accumulated & transferred the Pell funding is applied. #EdChat
Dr. Lasley: What makes #EarlyCollege unique is that college-level courses are combined w/ support services to help students succeed. #EdChat
Q: When does #EarlyCollege start? A: In some models students start as early as 9th and 10th grade, but it varies by school. #EdChat
Q: Are there certain colleges where students must transfer their credits? A: No. Students decide where to take their credits. #EdChat
